    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/15d7c6bf03d556aebad397ce3a38fd5f.poster.avif?t=1771016281\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/15d7c6bf03d556aebad397ce3a38fd5f.webm?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/15d7c6bf03d556aebad397ce3a38fd5f.mp4?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>征服小猫！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供5只不同的小猫，它们的属性和外观各不相同。通过通关解锁它们，并为它们命名。给它们喂食放射性牛奶，让它们变得更大更强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/f5e7dec54900d4b0235bab4f0c195ff2.poster.avif?t=1771016281\" width=600 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/f5e7dec54900d4b0235bab4f0c195ff2.webm?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/f5e7dec54900d4b0235bab4f0c195ff2.mp4?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>征服五大洲！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的猫配备了一件背心——在背心上建造一个激光装置。产生电力，将其存储在电池中并射击。使用旋转和移动的部件，攻击所有敌人。击败欧洲的鸽子、非洲的蛇和澳大利亚的蜘蛛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/8b543337ed39c8f9e93af13bd38bc740.poster.avif?t=1771016281\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/8b543337ed39c8f9e93af13bd38bc740.webm?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/8b543337ed39c8f9e93af13bd38bc740.mp4?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>照顾你的家！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >增加更多家具，购买花盆，种植缬草和猫薄荷。给植物浇水，然后为你的猫制作药水。购买更多的工作室设备，以解锁激光装置的其他部件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅行并摧毁！</p>",
